answers.answer: Sounds like typical pregnancy symptoms. How far along are you? Preeclampsia doesn't shop up until third trimester usually
I'm 37+2 weeks!
How's your blood pressure as of late?
I had it, didn't have symptoms until i went into Labor tho ):.
Hey I had preeclampsia with my first born its no joke my son and i almost died .  If it could be ask doctors to do protein test . as soon as possible
Last time it was checked was last Friday, andi it was normal, but all these symptoms didn't start till after!
I would call you doctor if your woried. They say if you have a prolonged headache  to call your doctor.

High blood pressure is the main sign and protein in your urine. I was just told my last visit that my last 3 urine tests had protein in them and i've continued to tell them each week that i'm extremely swollen. My blood pressure is ok though, so as of now i believe i am ok. If my blood pressure goes up then i will start to worry.im 37 weeks.
Those are symptoms of having Preeclampsia, but how's your blood pressure?
You need to go to the ER ASAP. I lost my nephew due to my sister having preeclampsia.
My doctor told me that there is a slight chance that i could possibly have preeclampsia again with this baby. & she said if so I would have to start seeing a High risk doctor .
The sooner you are given meds the better. How many weeks are you?

Sorry, I take my last two posts back. I just read you're 37 weeks. My sister was only 26 weeks when she had to have an emergency c-section due to the pain preeclampsia caused. I would call your doctor though and ask to be seen soon.
Last time my bp was checked was Friday and it was fine, bit I started to get all these symptoms Sunday!
I had protein in my urine a few ttimes with my daughter Christina in November and they want concerned what are the other reasons for protein in your urine

Hi. I had this with my daughter and we both nearly died. My symptoms started very much like this and by the time the hopsital got round to it I couldnt breath. It was like an elephant was sat on my chest.Please go and hget checked its not worth the ifs and buts . Good luck x
Alright thank you every one! I'm on my way to the hospital right now to get checked! I really hope everything is fine! :]
Good luck at the hospital, hoping everything is well with you and baby!

Maybe but it could also just be gestational hypertension. Its not preeclampsia until you have protein in your urine. Either way if you're worried you should call your dr and get your bp and urine checked. This my 2nd time with preeclamplsia and its no joke. Good luck!
Just saw your heading to the hospital. Wishing you all the best!

***UPDATE***Went to the hospital and bp is normal, no protein in the urine! But my midwife is really worried because of how horribly swollen I am and the headache I have had for 2 days! So I go back Friday to make sure everything is still fine! :]
That's great news! Wishing you good health.
